{"tid":1918814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵涌廣場現大量吉舖！人流減少多間小店告急 連譚仔三哥都租約期滿結業","createTime":"2020-03-10T10:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:14:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aec6bfbf872664329d10cbbc818e0e382cd74028","tid":1918814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1000end.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F1000end.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830&h=7aedf464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌廣場小食店、小店林立，成為一眾香港人的「掃街」之地，高峰時期三樓美食廣場人頭湧湧！不過早前有讀者去到葵廣時，就發現吉舖眾多，就連三樓的譚仔三哥都租約期滿，多間小店水盡鵝飛。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者指今星期，去到葵廣掃街，發現有不少食店和時裝店都結束營業，其中三樓更是重災區！不少平常看到的時裝店都變成吉舖，更有大部分店舖沒有開門做生意，而不少美食小店生意淡薄，人龍消失。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_7584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FIMG_7584.jpg&h=a17f4186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_7587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FIMG_7587.jpg&h=2ff04665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_7586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FIMG_7586.jpg&h=e35a46fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_7585.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FIMG_7585.jpg&h=6dd54118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_7589.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt